Syntax: go <direction> ...
2

2
Invokes the named exits in the named order, moving through many rooms in a single command.
2

2
Example:
2
Munchkin types:
2
  go n e e u e e s e
2
and moves quite rapidly from the Living Room all the way to the Bovine Illuminati Atrium, all in one command.
