46
2

2
- YOUR FIRST ROOM
2

2
  @dig "Turlit Room"
2

2
This first room isn't connected to anything else in the area.  Time to spruce the place up:
2

2
  @describe here as "Dank moldy tile room for turlits."
2

2
You can customize quite a few messages on your new room:
2

2
  @messages here
2
  @sit here is "You sit on the disgusting tile floor."
2

2
Any message can be set by adding a @ in front of it.
2
  @rise here is "You get up, wiping your hands on your ass."
2

2
(Wonder what those percent-sign symbols are in there?  'help pronouns')
2

2

2
- YOUR FIRST THING
2

2
Maybe we need an actual turlit.  Find one:
2

2
  @tree $furniture
2
      1 #30832   | | +-solid gold toilet        $  25000s1 / c7
2

2
  @create #30832 named "vile turlit,turlit"
2
  @describe turlit as "A brown turlit which smells of rotting afterbirths."
2
  drop turlit
2

2
As you might guess, '@messages turlit' will work.  Be sure to give your new thing some aliases (like 'turlit' for 'vile turlit', as above).  If you forgot:
2

2
  @addalias "turlit" to vile turlit
2

2
If you're just sick of the whole damn thing:
2

2
