            |   /+y NORTH      space. If you want to sound 
2
            |  /               incredibly geeky you can tell 
2
  WEST      | /                your friends this.
2
    -x      |/
2
     <------|------>           Positive directions:
2
           /|     +x EAST       Up, North, and East
2
          / |                  
2
         /  |                  Negative directions:
2
      -y/   | -z                Down, South, and West
2
   SOUTH    v DOWN
