2
Syntax:   hashremove( HASH a_hash, STR|OBJ|INT|FLOAT|ERR key ) => HASH
2

2
  Returns a copy of a_hash, with key removed if it exists.
2

2
Errors:
2
  E_TYPE:   if the types of the given arguments are invalid.
