2
Syntax:   keys   ( HASH a_hash ) => LIST
2
          values ( HASH a_hash ) => LIST
2

2
  Returns a list of the keys (or values) in a_hash.
2

2
Errors:
2
  E_TYPE:   if a_hash isn't a hash.
