2
Syntax:  @locations object
2

2
Prints out the names and object numbers of all containing objects.
2

2
Example:
2
  @locations ur-Rog
2
  ur-Rog(#6349)   ur-Rog's Display Case(#6355)   Editorial Boardroom(#5747)
