2
Saving. Please do not turn off the MOO.
2
Everything begins to glow around you, as you realize you have discovered the key to the meani-- oh wait, it was just the drugs again--
2
The server bites! The server bites! The server bites! You checkpoint...
2
You get a strange feeling of deja vu.
2
The world grows dim, you feel your heart stop in your chest, and noises grow distant... and then you burp.
2
Error reading disk in drive A:
2
LOAD "*",8
2
A horrible stench permeates your nostrils.
2
How... how could this have happened?!
2
Grab a beer every time you see this message.
2
Buhhhh durrrrr.
2
You sneeze.  That feeling of relief seems to come half a second later.
2
Your genitals swell for a fraction of a second.
2
Did everything just freeze in place for a moment?  That was odd.
2
You could swear your surroundings flipped upside-down for just a moment.
2
You get your left hand confused with your right. Ha, weird.
2
You yawn, seized by a sudden lethargy.
2
You get the curious feeling that you've never been here before.
2
Your immersion breaks for a second...
2
You hear a high pitched whine of disk platters spinning, far in the distance.
2
Everything goes...pixelated? for a brief moment, then snaps back to reality.
2
Things get all... FUNNY.
2
It's dangerous outside. Take this.
2
I have a bad feeling about this...
2
You're, like... freakin' out, man.
2
Oh.. oh god. They're everywhere! Crawling all over you! In your hair!
2
They're coming up the god damn walls!
