2

2
The number one rule is: HAVE FUN! All the other rules are basically to make sure that everyone can follow the first rule. Please see:
2

2
help grinding
2
help griefing
2
help crime
2
help bugs
2
help spoilers
2

2
Note that just because there is no written rule against something it isn't automatically alright. Admins have the authority to dispense justice as they see fit. If you're being a jerk, dick, asshole, or retard you may find yourself with an unpleasant surprise.
