Hello and welcome! This document is a guide to common etiquette one must be familiar with to have any chance of surviving in the vicious and unforgiving world of HellMOO. While you might initially shrug common courtesies off as being no of concern to you, you must understand that sometimes the correct etiquette can mean the difference between living as care free a life as possible and dying repeatedly to someone who has taken offense to you!
2

2
The first thing we should mention while talking about manners are those that must be employed while engaging in a rousing bout of Player vs Player (or pvp for short!) combat. Nobody likes a sore loser or a cocky winner, so be sure to be those things in the correct situation! If you managed to kill someone, the next step is clearly to send them pages telling them what a sissy faggot they are and that they should just kill themselves for sucking so bad. If you have just been killed by another player, quickly start yelling at them in chatnet for being a griefing cocksucker! The more people that know about this travesty the better. If they really gave it to you good, be sure to go that extra mile and page an admin to let them personally know.
2

2
That brings us to the next thing we must mention: Griefing. If someone has said something in chatnet to slightly irritate you, or you are just feeling moody that day, the immediate remedy for this is to hunt them down and kill them repeatedly. As long as the cops don't see you do it, it's okay! Ignore any complaints the victim makes, because lets face it, they should just get stronger so they can kill you back. It's their fault, you see.
2

2
------------------
2
FUN FACT: Griefing will make Gilmore love you!
2
------------------
2

2
But sometimes, you may not wish to be involved in any conflict. The best way to go about this is to first type chatnet off and avoid any interaction with other players in the world. You may be offered an invitation into a corporation. THIS IS A TRAP! Do not accept any offers of this sort. When the big kids of a rival corporation get irritated with someone in your corporation, you WILL be targeted. If you have fallen into this trap and are now in this situation, you might try reasoning with your mindless aggressors, but this is unlikely to get you anywhere.
2

2
------------------
2
Frank says, Hi Bob, would you like to join my corporation and be friends?
2
'WRONG' : Bob says, Sure Frank, I'd love to. This will allow me to have a fulfilling part in this intricate social structure.
2
'RIGHT' : Bob says, No hablo ingles.
2
------------------
2

2
So you've either just killed another player or stumbled onto their corpse, undoubtedly killed by a chud or some such. Then the moral dilemma hits you, cue the faggot tiny angel and devil. Do you take this poor schmuck's hard earned possessions? On the one hand, he was probably a nazi. But then again, do you really need another 4 cans of Mingus Dew, a firearms assembly, a plastic athletic cup, a denim skirt, a pink tamagotchi, and a combat knife? Chances are you don't but hey, finders keepers. Just make sure you don't get caught taking it all, assuming you didn't kill him, and that nazi will never know to come after you. And if you did kill him to be able to take it all, he's all that much less likely to kill you to take it back. Trust me, that Hitler wannabe deserved it. Fuck his corpse while you're at it.
2

2
Speaking of sex, there are a few common courtesies you should know off hand. The first rule of thumb for sex in Hell is that everyone likes it. Some people may not have set their preferences to allow it, but that is just them playing hard to get! The second rule of thumb for sex in Hell is that yiffing is better than normal sex. As much as they love a good dicking, anyone is sure to go mad for a gent in a fur suit who is ready for a long bout of furtacular action. But what's this you say? You've knocked your partner up and you're not sure what course of action to take? The mannerly thing to do is to locate a wire hanger and fix the problem right up. We all know you're not going to be paying child support to that whore and really, the last thing this place needs is more brats running around.
2

2
------------------
2
'WRONG' : Bob says, Hello sir, would you like to engage in consensual procreation with me?
2
'RIGHT' : Bob says, hey faggot here comes my cock!!!
2
------------------
2

2
There are certain types of people that require different approaches in your etiquette towards them. The first of whom is someone who has disconnected and left their character out in the open. Your first instinct might be to pinch them, and send them on home. While it is a nice thing to do, it is much more polite to kill them and take all of their possessions. It is a lesson they will be sure to remember for the future when they have more expensive equipment and, even better, they will never know it was you. Should the player merely be idling, similar actions should be taken, but there is a higher risk that your politeness will be returned.
2

2
Then there is the scripter. They are the ones who will sit in the gym or other areas suitable for skill ups and allow triggers to mine IPs for them. The courteous thing to do is exactly what you think it is. Either kill or kidnap them. If you are afraid of retaliation, explosives are extremely handy for this! You are doing both them and the rest of the community a service in this action. After all, you wouldn't want a script playing this fine game for you, would you? I thought not.
2

2
And finally, there are the sort of people who prefer to roleplay their characters. They are faggots, but in the interest of keeping yourself alive, it is best to stick to the previous rules when dealing with them, and for the most part attempt to ignore them. If you find yourself unable to avoid interaction with one of this breed, it is highly recommended that you speak in olde english and look for a way out of the situation as quickly as possible. Fortunately, if you keep your wits about you a situation like that is uncommon.
2

2
Now that you have read this guide, you should have all the social skills you need to make it in this Hell we all share. Get out there and rejoice in your newfound ability to not be killed the moment you open, or don't open, your mouth!
