Despite your constant ridiculous deaths and recloning, your character does have an age, which gradually increases (the stress of imperfect cloning lets this happen. Damn technology!) Type '@age' to see it, along with the length of real-world time your character has existed.
2

2
Every player starts as a 13-year old kid. You'll gradually get older -- mostly through dying. Every death will age your character a little more. The more mutated you are, the harder it is for the cloning machine to reproduce you, and the faster you'll age.
2

2
It's rumored that the effects of aging can be reversed with strange homemade drugs.
