To allow someone to do something, just type something like ~1b[1m~1b[37mallow ~1b[1mcocoon~1b[22m from FriendlyGuy~1b[22m~1b[36m. To take it back, ~1b[1m~1b[37mdeny ~1b[1mcocoon~1b[22m from FriendlyGuy~1b[22m~1b[36m . Remember, allows by itself will show everything you allow or deny.
