2
In the apocalyptic world of tomorrow, the world has only one thing in common: the money system. (That, and mutants roam everywhere, and you can ~1b[1mfight~1b[22m anybody and anything, but bear with me, okay?)
2

2
In HellMOO, no one has any paper cash, and rarely do people barter. Instead, there is but one currency, and that is digital ~1b[1mcredits.~1b[22m To use ~1b[1mcredits,~1b[22m every human has a wristpad that displays ~1b[1mcredits~1b[22m and ~1b[1mallows~1b[22m transfer of them between wristpads (and can ~1b[1mtell~1b[22m ~1b[1mtime,~1b[22m ~1b[1mgive~1b[22m you a map of the area, but let's focus on the money part.)
2

2
To take a ~1b[1mlook~1b[22m at how much money you have, type ~1b[1m~1b[37msu~1b[22m~1b[36m. This is like ~1b[1m~1b[37mst~1b[22m~1b[36m but much shorter!
2

2
[|||||||||||||| ] XP: 2071 $31,400
2

2
Your ~1b[1mhealth,~1b[22m spendable ~1b[1mXP,~1b[22m and money are shown in that order.
2

2
Money is used for a lot of things; usually, you'll use it to buy stuff from merchants. To buy something, go in their ~1b[1mstore~1b[22m and type ~1b[1m~1b[37mlist~1b[22m~1b[36m to see what they have to offer. To actually buy something, type ~1b[1m~1b[37mbuy <item>~1b[22m~1b[36m and, if you have enough ~1b[1mcredits,~1b[22m you'll buy it. You can also buy things from automats; if you find one, ~1b[1m~1b[37mexam automat~1b[22m~1b[36m to find out how to use it.
2

2
Money is useful for lots of other things -- ~1b[1mlearning~1b[22m ~1b[1mskills~1b[22m from NPC ~1b[1mteachers,~1b[22m paying Kharn not to cut your head off and ~1b[1mfuck~1b[22m the stump...the list goes on. To pay a human player, type ~1b[1m~1b[37mpay <amount> to <player>~1b[22m~1b[36m. If the player isn't actually in the room, use ~1b[1m~1b[1m~1b[37mpaypal~1b[22m <amount> to <player>~1b[22m~1b[36m -- unfortunately ~1b[1mpaypal~1b[22m takes a 5% transaction fee. Jerks!
2

2
So, how do you earn money? Lots of ways.
2

2
There are numerous ~1b[1mNPCs~1b[22m walking in town. Go up to them and ask what they need.
2

2
~1b[1m~1b[37m-69Jane Whaddya need?~1b[22m~1b[36m
2
Casull [to 69Jane]: Whaddya need?
2
