The first thing we should mention while ~1b[1mtalking~1b[22m about ~1b[1mmanners~1b[22m are those that must be employed while engaging in a rousing bout of Player vs Player (or ~1b[1mpvp~1b[22m for short!) ~1b[1mcombat.~1b[22m Nobody likes a sore loser or a cocky winner, so be sure to be those things in the correct situation! If you managed to ~1b[1mkill~1b[22m someone, the next step is clearly to send them pages telling them what a sissy faggot they are and that they should just ~1b[1mkill~1b[22m themselves for sucking so bad. If you have just been killed by another player, quickly start yelling at them in ~1b[1mchatnet~1b[22m for being a ~1b[1mgriefing~1b[22m cocksucker! The more people that know about this travesty the better. If they really gave it to you good, be sure to go that extra mile and ~1b[1mpage~1b[22m an admin to let them personally know.
