But sometimes, you may not wish to be involved in any conflict. The best way to go about this is to first type ~1b[1mchatnet~1b[22m off and avoid any interaction with other players in the world. You may be offered an invitation into a corporation. THIS IS A TRAP! Do not accept any offers of this sort. When the big kids of a rival corporation get irritated with someone in your corporation, you WILL be targeted. If you have fallen into this trap and are now in this situation, you might try reasoning with your mindless aggressors, but this is unlikely to get you anywhere.
