There are a number of options to change your gameplay ~1b[1mexperience,~1b[22m accessible via the ~1b[1m~1b[1m~1b[37m@prefs~1b[22m~1b[36m~1b[22m command. Type ~1b[1m~1b[1m~1b[37m@prefs~1b[22m~1b[36m~1b[22m to see a list of options and your current ~1b[1msettings~1b[22m for them.
