2
~1b[1m~1b[37m *~1b[22m~1b[36m ansihack -- Some MOO clients don't respond to certain ANSI (color) codes. If you notice that colors seem to be leaking (things are bold when they aren't supposed to be, things are inconsistently colored, etc.,) turn this on to see if it helps.
2
~1b[1m~1b[37m *~1b[22m~1b[36m singlecolumn -- This changes your inventory listing, and the list of contents of containers, so that each item appears on a line by itself, rather than the default two-per-line display.
