To adjust a preference, use ~1b[1m~1b[1m~1b[37m@prefs~1b[22m <preference> is <value>~1b[22m~1b[36m. For example, ~1b[1m~1b[1m~1b[37m@prefs~1b[22m map is 0~1b[22m~1b[36m. (Note: Not recommended. The map is very handy.)
