Eschaton Outfitters (EO) in FC sell two helpful items: climbing ropes and grappling hooks. Climbing ropes ~1b[1mmake~1b[22m a climb easier, but can only be hung down from the top of a climb with ~1b[1m~1b[37mhang rope from <exit>~1b[22m~1b[36m. Grappling hooks can be thrown to the top of a climb, but are significantly more expensive.
