Welcome to what used to be the most boring grind in HellMOO, now made FUN,
2
AWESOME, EPIC, and CUSTOMIZABLE! LET'S GET PUMPED UP! IT'S LIKE YOU ORGASM
2
WITH EVERY REP!
2

2
You've probably typed ~1b[1mscore~1b[22m or ~1b[1msc~1b[22m at some point after rolling. And noticed
2
that up on the top of that scoresheet, you've got some ~1b[1mstats.~1b[22m You've got your
2
brawn, for beating shit up, your reflexes, for beating shit up faster, your
2
brains, for beating shit up smarter, your...alright, we know what it's all for.
2

2
But maybe you're not happy with just that many stat points. Maybe you want
2
more. Maybe the ~1b[1mmutations~1b[22m you've picked up aren't enough. That's why we train.
2
We go out there and grind our ~1b[1mstats~1b[22m up, liftin those weights, hittin that
2
speed bag, smackin the juke box...all of that.
2

2
Now, the way this works, is simple. There's machines throughout the world.
2
Some of these machines, when you ~1b[1mexamine~1b[22m them, you'll see you can do actions,
2
do reps on them, something. And this'll exercise your ~1b[1mstats.~1b[22m You'll gain ~1b[1mIP~1b[22m
2
in them (100 ~1b[1mIP~1b[22m equals +1 to a stat, by the way, or a skill if you're ~1b[1mgrinding~1b[22m
2
that), at the cost of a little ~1b[1mXP,~1b[22m and it'll eventually go up.
2
=======
2
The machines for Brawn, Reflexes, and Endurance are all in the Slagtown ~1b[1mGym.~1b[22m
2
There's also a cardiogram here that shows you your limits.
2

2
The jukebox in Any Port - as well as any other you can find - exercises your
2
Cool. Take a ~1b[1mlook~1b[22m at it, you should be able to figure out how.
2

2
There's ~1b[1mrumors~1b[22m of a computer underneath the sewers, in the Subway tunnels or
2
lower, that can exercise your brains.
2

2
And lastly, word is that video game arcades are the place to go if you want
2
to raise your senses.
2
======
2
Now, the limits. There's always limits. There's three limits here, in fact. The
2
first is the amount of training you can do - total. You can gain 800 ~1b[1mIP~1b[22m total
2
in your entire life. That's +8 to your ~1b[1mstats.~1b[22m Don't be stupid. You don't get
2
any good from half a point in a stat. And nobody's going to fix it for you.
2
But, don't worry. The 800 ~1b[1mIP~1b[22m limit only counts for the machines listed here.
2
If your Reflexes goes up because you stabbed something, it's not going to mean
2
you can't do less on the machines.
2

2
Next, you can only get 30 ~1b[1mIP~1b[22m from the machines a game-week. Just so you know,
2
some creepy guy told me that means 21 hours out there in the real world~1b[22m~1b[36m.
2
I don't know what he's smoking, I thought Freedom City WAS the Real World.
2
And I haven't had a hit of crank in minutes.
2

2
Lastly, you can't get a stat above 18 by training. ~1b[1mMutations~1b[22m don't count, if
2
you've wandered over some odd ~1b[1mradiation~1b[22m somewhere and wanged up your DNA, but
2
none of this trainin til you can punch through sheet metal. You're going
2
to need ~1b[1mmutations~1b[22m and ~1b[1mimplants~1b[22m to do that too.
2

2
Now, go out there and grind up those ~1b[1mstats.~1b[22m Have fun.
