If you don't have your health, what DO you have?
2

2
Health is precious. You've got a bar full of it (type ~1b[1m~1b[37mst~1b[22m~1b[36m to see it). When people beat on you, or you fall off a cliff, or starve, or get irradiated, or whatever -- you'll lose health. When it hits zero, you'll die.
2

2
How do you get it back? Several ways, in order of decreasing convenience:
2

2
~1b[1m~1b[37m *~1b[22m~1b[36m Use a nanite healer. (Takes a little medic skill)
2
~1b[1m~1b[37m *~1b[22m~1b[36m Use a trauma kit. (Takes more medic skill)
2
~1b[1m~1b[37m *~1b[22m~1b[36m Have ~1b[1msex~1b[22m or eat ~1b[1mfood,~1b[22m then sit or lie down for a while. (Can be slow)
2

2
You can even increase your maximum health through the use of endocrine boosters, buyable in the corpclave.
2

2
See also: ~1b[1mhelp~1b[22m ~1b[1millness,~1b[22m ~1b[1mhelp~1b[22m medic
