You can ~1b[1mstore~1b[22m a list of friends, the primary purpose of which is to assist in specifying permissions (see ~1b[1mhelp~1b[22m allows). For example you may want to allow your friends to ~1b[1mhelp~1b[22m you: ~1b[1m~1b[37mallow medical from friends~1b[22m~1b[36m ).
