Despite your constant ridiculous deaths and recloning, your character does have an age, which gradually increases (the ~1b[1mstress~1b[22m of imperfect ~1b[1mcloning~1b[22m lets this happen. Damn technology!) Type ~1b[1m~1b[37m@age~1b[22m~1b[36m to see it, along with the length of real-world ~1b[1mtime~1b[22m your character has existed.
2

2
Every player starts as a 13-year old kid. You'll gradually get older -- mostly through dying. Every ~1b[1mdeath~1b[22m will age your character a little more. The more mutated you are, the harder it is for the ~1b[1mcloning~1b[22m machine to reproduce you, and the faster you'll age.
