To allow someone to do something, just type something like allow ~1b[1mcocoon~1b[22m from FriendlyGuy. To take it back, deny ~1b[1mcocoon~1b[22m from FriendlyGuy . ~1b[1mRemember,~1b[22m allows by itself will show everything you allow or deny.
2

2
Keep in mind there's a reason this system exists -- most of these actions could injure or even kill you if done by a malicious person! Don't allow people to do things to you just because they asked.
