As you might have noticed, time passes in the world of HellMOO, and it doesn't map directly to the time in the "real world" (whatever that is).  Time in Hell flows at 8 times the speed of real time -- every 24 hours of realtime, 8 game days pass.
2

2
You can see what time it is by looking at your wristpad, or just typing 'time'.  The time of day affects many things -- lots of shops are only open certain hours, vampires don't want to be out during the day, many NPCs have daily schedules, etc.
