So, what do you ~1b[1mlook~1b[22m like? What do you want other players to see when they ~1b[1mlook~1b[22m at you? To describe yourself, type ~1b[1m~1b[1m~1b[37m@describe~1b[22m me as <description>~1b[22m~1b[36m or ~1b[1m~1b[37m@desc me as <description>~1b[22m~1b[36m.
2

2
Whatever you type is what people will see when they use the ~1b[1m~1b[1m~1b[37mlook~1b[22m~1b[36m~1b[22m command on you.
2

2
Example:
2
Ammut types:
2
~1b[1m~1b[1m~1b[37m@describe~1b[22m me as "More like a ham than a man, really."~1b[22m~1b[36m
2
People who type ~1b[1m~1b[1m~1b[37mlook~1b[22m Ammut~1b[22m~1b[36m now see:
2
More like a ham than a man, really.
2

2
You are encouraged to be creative. You can also describe your nude body parts with ~1b[1m~1b[1m~1b[37m@nude~1b[22m <part> is <description>~1b[22m~1b[36m, which will show whenever that part of your body is uncovered.
2

2
Example: ~1b[1m~1b[1m~1b[37m@nude~1b[22m back is "%P back is covered in horrible burn scars."~1b[22m~1b[36m Here "%P" is replaced with "His", "Her", or "Its" depending on your gender. See ~1b[1m~1b[1m~1b[37mhelp~1b[22m ~1b[1mpronouns~1b[22m~1b[36m~1b[22m for ~1b[1mhelp~1b[22m on using that (it does not work with ~1b[1m~1b[1m~1b[37m@describe~1b[22m~1b[36m,~1b[22m only in the nude body part descriptions).
2

2
Note: Do not use descriptions (@nude or otherwise) to pretend you have things you don't (for example, using the worn descriptions for various pieces of ~1b[1marmor~1b[22m in-game, etc.). ~1b[1mDoing~1b[22m this will at least get your description privileges removed, or possibly banned.
