Hello, newbie!  Confused?  You probably are.
2

2
The first place you'll want to go (that is, if you want to KILL) is the orphanage, marked as '<=' on your map.  This is where all new players start, so you're probably there already!  If not, type 'lmap' to get a local map, complete with a legend, and head there.  If you don't remember how to move, just type the direction you want to move in.  You can get a good look at your surroundings by typing 'look'.  To attack something, type 'kill <target>'.  Gosh, this game is easy after all!
