So you want to be a super-scientist!  That's commendable.  Science in HellMOO allows you to use weapons such as proton packs, and such neat items as portalguns.  More importantly, though, it allows you to use the simulators to find schematics for making all sorts of fun stuff indeed. There are other fun scientific exploits to be done out there, so let's learn some Science!
2

2
It should be noted that many science skill-enhancing activities are associated with elements of extreme danger.  Before attempting them, you should probably take a lesson or two on science.  Dr. Spengler in CSICOP can teach you, if you can prove you're dedicated to science.
2

2
Rumor has it that many of our most prominent scientists started on that path after a run-in with Corpclave security.
