OH GOD YOU'RE ON FIRE.  Now what?
2

2
Fire hurts.  Depending on how much you're burning, you'll either take little damage or take a whole lotta damage, unless you have the firewalker mutation (You don't take any damage with firewalker.)  You also lose a bit of cool, depending on how much you're burning, and you'll feel hot (not sexy-hot, I mean literally hot.)
2

2
You have several ways of putting out a fire: You can either douse yourself in water, run into a shower, or type 'roll'.  When you roll, you'll keep rolling till your fire's out - useful, but slow.
