2
NPCs (non player characters) are creatures just like yourself, with their own lives and (sometimes) goals and behaviors.
2

2
You can converse with an NPC just like you would a player -- talk to them with directed speech:
2

2
   -care Hi there dawg!
2
   Timmy [to Care Dog]: Hi there dawg!
2

2
Not sure what to say to them?  Start with 'hello' or 'hi'.  You'll notice that some words in their replies are in 'bold' -- this is a hint that you could ask them about that topic and have more conversation.  Not everything an NPC knows about will be shown this way, so if you think an NPC might know about something, it's worth a try to ask.
2

2
You can do lots of other things with various NPCs (besides kill them).  For instance, with ganglanders and slagtownies you can 'ask <npc> about <player>' to persuade them to give up some information about another player.
