Have an idea to contribute to the game? Want to see something added? Have new and refreshing ways of being a sick pervert? The *ideas mailing list is here to serve YOU!
2

2
Type '@qsend *ideas' and enter your topic and message, then end it with '.' on its own line to send the message.  To read it, '@subscribe *ideas', then '@next on *ideas' to keep reading that list.
2

2
But wait! There's more! You can vote on the ideas you like or hate!  '@yes <number> on *ideas' will let us know that you like it, and '@no <number> on *ideas' will register your complete disgust with that horribly stupid idea that should never be implemented ever.
2

2
You can also '@comment <number> on *ideas' to add your own comments to that post.
2

2
See also:  help mail, help communication
