Unlike many other MUDs, roleplaying on HellMOO is most definitely NOT required.  In fact, almost the entire playerbase is hostile to the idea of "roleplaying" in the traditional sense and will actively pick on you for it.
2

2
However, you'll start to notice that almost all serious hell players 'roleplay' to some extent, in the sense of getting involved in the reality of the actions your player is taking and the interactions you're having with the world and other players.  That's the kind of roleplaying we try to encourage, as opposed to the traditional "I'm a bitter wasteland bounty hunter whose parents were killed by ninjas!" roleplaying.
2

2
So feel free to get really into being that teenage mutant with a black leather jacket and dual pistols and a grudge against chuds.
