~1b[1m~1b[37m *~1b[22m~1b[36m ~1b[1m~1b[37m@attach <msg> on <list> <object>~1b[22m~1b[36m
2
... attach a reference of an object to a post, e.g. for bug reporting
2

2
To see votes and comments on these mailing ~1b[1mlists~1b[22m as they happen, just type ~1b[1m~1b[37mmailnet on~1b[22m~1b[36m to start receiving notifications. To turn it off, just type ~1b[1m~1b[37mmailnet off~1b[22m~1b[36m. ~1b[1m~1b[37mmailnet ~1b[1mhistory~1b[22m~1b[36m~1b[22m also works just like on any other net.
2

2
There is also a way to read specific sets of messages, instead of single messages or groups. In every command where you'd usually put a message number, you can put what are called ~1b[1m~1b[37mmessage sequence keywords':
2
~1b[1m~1b[37m *~1b[22m~1b[36m ~1b[1m~1b[37mfrom:playername~1b[22m~1b[36m .. messages only from player named playername.
2
~1b[1m~1b[37m *~1b[22m~1b[36m ~1b[1m~1b[37msubject:text~1b[22m~1b[36m ..... messages with text in the subject line
2
~1b[1m~1b[37m *~1b[22m~1b[36m ~1b[1m~1b[37mbody:text~1b[22m~1b[36m ........ messages with text in the message body
2
~1b[1m~1b[37m *~1b[22m~1b[36m ~1b[1m~1b[37mbefore:date~1b[22m~1b[36m ...... only messages sent before date
2
~1b[1m~1b[37m *~1b[22m~1b[36m ~1b[1m~1b[37mafter:date~1b[22m~1b[36m ....... only messages sent after date
2
~1b[1m~1b[37m *~1b[22m~1b[36m ~1b[1m~1b[37msince:date~1b[22m~1b[36m ....... messages on or after date
2
~1b[1m~1b[37m *~1b[22m~1b[36m ~1b[1m~1b[37muntil:date~1b[22m~1b[36m ....... messages before or on date
2
~1b[1m~1b[37m *~1b[22m~1b[36m ~1b[1m~1b[37mlast:n~1b[22m~1b[36m ........... only the last n messages
2

2
When searching by date, you may specify today, yesterday, lastweek, lastmonth, lastyear, or a specific date. Dates must be specified in the format DD-MMM-YYYY (examples: 9-Sep-2010, 18-Feb-2004).
2

2
For voting / status-tracking ~1b[1mlists,~1b[22m there are more:
2
~1b[1m~1b[37m *~1b[22m~1b[36m ~1b[1m~1b[37mcomment:text~1b[22m~1b[36m ....... messages with text in a comment
2
~1b[1m~1b[37m *~1b[22m~1b[36m ~1b[1m~1b[37mminvotes:n~1b[22m~1b[36m ......... messages with at least n total votes
2
~1b[1m~1b[37m *~1b[22m~1b[36m ~1b[1m~1b[37mminscore:n~1b[22m~1b[36m ......... messages ~1b[1mwith~1b[22m score (plus - minus) n or more
2
~1b[1m~1b[37m *~1b[22m~1b[36m ~1b[1m~1b[37mtype:sometype~1b[22m~1b[36m ...... messages that are some type
2
~1b[1m~1b[37m *~1b[22m~1b[36m ~1b[1m~1b[37mtype:notsometype~1b[22m~1b[36m ... all messages that aren't some type
2
~1b[1m~1b[37m *~1b[22m~1b[36m ~1b[1m~1b[37mstatus:somestatus~1b[22m~1b[36m .. messages that are ~1b[1msome~1b[22m status
2
~1b[1m~1b[37m *~1b[22m~1b[36m ~1b[1m~1b[37mstatus:notx~1b[22m~1b[36m ........ all messages that aren't x
2
~1b[1m~1b[37m *~1b[22m~1b[36m ~1b[1m~1b[37massigned:admin~1b[22m~1b[36m ..... messages assigned to that admin
2
(use ~1b[1m~1b[37mnone~1b[22m~1b[36m for unassigned)
2

2
You can even combine these keywords for complex results. Examples:
2
~1b[1m~1b[37m *~1b[22m~1b[36m ~1b[1m~1b[37m@read last:10 on *ideas~1b[22m~1b[36m -- see the last 10 messages on *ideas
2
~1b[1m~1b[37m *~1b[22m~1b[36m ~1b[1m~1b[37m@read last:100 minscore:3 on *ideas~1b[22m~1b[36m -- out of the last 100 messages on *ideas, show me only those with a ~1b[1mscore~1b[22m of 3 or greater.
2
~1b[1m~1b[37m *~1b[22m~1b[36m ~1b[1m~1b[37m@mail status:implemented on *ideas~1b[22m~1b[36m -- see a list of *ideas that are implemented.
2
~1b[1m~1b[37m *~1b[22m~1b[36m ~1b[1m~1b[37m@mail status:open body:hamburger from:me on *bug~1b[22m~1b[36m -- see messages on *bugs that are from me, Open ~1b[1mstatus,~1b[22m and mention hamburger.
2

