So you want to pick locks eh?  I'm sure you just lost your key, or maybe you're helping out a friend.  You certainly wouldn't want to be committing a crime!
2

2
Ahem.  Anyway.  As you could guess, picking locks is a crime, so prepare to deal with the cops if you do this in front of a camera.  To pick a lock you're going to need some kind of lockpick device.  There are two kinds of locks -- physical locks (like key locks or combination locks), and electronic locks (like VoxGuards or scanlocks).  Physical locks need a physical pick, like a potmetal or titanium lockpick, and your success will depend on your locksmith skill.  Electronic locks need an electronic pick like a magspike, and your success depends on BOTH your locksmith AND your hack skill.
2

2
Once you've got your pick and you're in front of the door, just 'pick <door>' and away you go!  You can only try a given lock every so often, so make it count; juice your skills to the max with drugs or whatever else you like.  Take off your gloves to ensure success.
2

2
When you're just starting out you'll probably want to find a nice easy out-of-the-way lock with no cameras around to practice on.  Try the Sharpton Projects or one of the consumer apartments like Xolair or Humatrope.  You can make yourself a nice supply of potmetal lockpicks in prison.  Happy picking!
