What's that smell?!
2

2
Smells play a fairly minor role in Hell life.  You can just 'smell' to get a whiff of what's smelling interesting in your current location; this probably doesn't tell you anything you didn't already know.
2

2
You can also 'smell <drink>' to see if it smells like poison or chemicals, or 'smell <food>' to see if the food's rotten.  This is only slightly more useful.
