You can give items in your inventory to other players or NPCs:
2

2
'give <item> to <person>'
2

2
They won't necessarily accept them!  Most NPCs aren't interested in stupid junk you found lying around.  Some consumers wandering around might want food, drink, or drugs from you -- ask them about their needs to find out.  Some NPCs might be looking for specific items you can give them.
2

2
Players won't accept items you give them, unless they allow gifts from you.
2

2
See also: help allows, help npcs
