There are many, many different mailing lists in this game. 'help mail' listed six of them. Here is a longer list of the lists that are actually used.
2

2
'LISTS TO WHICH YOU CAN READ AND WRITE:'
2
 - '*bugs' - Quite possibly the most used list. If something is bugged or otherwise not working correctly, send it here. Before sending, though, consider whether your issue relates to something that's outright broken or just something that's unbalanced. If the latter, make a post to '*game-reports' (see below) instead.
2
 - '*ideas' - If you have an idea for a new thing or an improvement on an existing thing, send it to this list. Remember, if it's a balance suggestion, send it to '*game-reports' as explained above. Don't consistently send dumb *ideas posts or you might get banned.
2
 - '*game-reports' (AKA *gr, *g-r, *game, and *whine-reports) - This here list is for stuff like \"mutation X could be better, here are some reasons why\" or \"monster Y isn't giving enough XP, here are some reasons why\" or \"area Z is far too dangerous, here are some reasons why\" and so on. Please make sure to back up your posts with your experiences related to the topic at hand! We, the admins, need to know what's wrong with something before we can possibly fix it.
2
 - '*comedy' - This list is for things that happen in-game that you think are funny (this includes posts on other lists, chatnet/zotnet/corpchat quotes, etc.). If you're not sure whether something is funny or not, the wiki has a very helpful guide at http://hellmoo.org/wiki/index.php/So_you_want_to_post_to_%2AComedy on deciding whether or not to post.
2
 - '*chatter' - For general shit talk about whatever. This list isn't used very often, but please feel free to use it some more.
2
 - '*food' - For talking about the food you eat IRL. Slightly more popular than *chatter.
2
 - '*forbes' - For corporation CEOs to make "official" posts. Everyone can read this, but you cannot post to this unless you are one of your corp's holders.
2
 - '*shenanigans' - This list is for all the "wacky" shit that you did that even we (the admins) didn't expect could be done with the game.
2

2
'LISTS WHICH YOU CAN ONLY READ:'
2
 - '*changelog-public' (AKA *clp) - The list where we post major (and often not-so-major) changes to the game. The automatic daily changelog (collecting the fixed bugs and implemented ideas from other lists) is also posted here. If you subscribe to only one mailing list, MAKE IT THIS ONE.
2
 - '*rumors' - For when we make changes, but want the post regarding them to sound more immersive or some shit. Basically the same as *clp but not used as often.
2
 - '*crime-and-punishment' (AKA *cap and *cnp) - When a player gets scrambled or otherwise banned, his or her offenses will usually be posted to this list. Don't do what these people did!
2

2
'LISTS TO WHICH YOU CAN WRITE, BUT CANNOT READ:'
2
- '*custom-requests' - Send a post here if you have an idea for a custom item (some sort of clothing, a renamed weapon, almost all sorts of other things). You can also post here if you want a namechange (these requests are not taken lightly) or if you want one of your messages ('@messages me' to see which ones you can change, no dumb requests or else bad things will happen) changed. Be prepared to pay out the ass should we grant your request.
2
 - '*exploit-reports' - Found some sort of exploitable bug? Post it here. This way, the less scrupulous of players won't be able to exploit it before we fix it.
2
 - '*Appeal to Authority' (AKA *ata) - Are you and a friend/family member/etc. playing HellMOO from the same place? Send a post here explaining it. Think someone is abusing alts? Tattle on him or her with this list. Basically, this list is for any sort of GM-ish issues which need to be brought to our attention.
2
 - '*admin-abuse' - Has a badmin been unreasonably fucking with you (believe it or not, it happens)? Send a post here detailing what happened. Note that this is for major abuses on our part. That is to say, don't come crying here if you get zotted after doing something dumb on zotnet.
2
  - '*programmers' - Our internal list for discussion of various admin things. Stay the hell away from this list unless an admin has told you to post to it or if you know what the fuck you're doing. Making dumb posts here will probably get you banned.
2

2
'A NOTE ON USING THE LISTS:' Always use the asterisk (that's the * symbol, smart guy) before the name of the list. Otherwise the mail system will assume you want to send something to a player by that name and will only reach that list if no player matches said name. This caused a lot of rage back when a legit newbie by the name of Bugster joined the game, as he received many posts that would have otherwise gone to *bugs (and many subsequent death threats, most likely).
2

2
'ANOTHER NOTE:' The command '@unsubscribed' will show you all the lists in the game. Many of them are depreciated or are otherwise used only by the admins; as such, they were not listed in this list. For the curious among you, some of them contain information and changes from the early days of HellMOO.
