No, no, no. That is not how the ~1b[1mhelp~1b[22m system works. You don't type ~1b[1m~1b[1m~1b[37mhelp~1b[22m topic~1b[22m~1b[36m (or ~1b[1m~1b[1m~1b[37mhelp~1b[22m ~1b[1m<topic>~1b[22m~1b[36m~1b[22m or whatever it is that you just typed). You type ~1b[1m~1b[1m~1b[37mhelp~1b[22m <insert the name of the topic that you actually want right here>~1b[22m~1b[36m.
