We're always looking for a few likeminded souls to ~1b[1mhelp~1b[22m us polish the silverware and take out the trash. Are you:
2

2
~1b[1m~1b[37m *~1b[22m~1b[36m Capable of writing English sentences with correct spelling and punctuation?
2
~1b[1m~1b[37m *~1b[22m~1b[36m Lacking in social ~1b[1mskills?~1b[22m
2
~1b[1m~1b[37m *~1b[22m~1b[36m Experienced with some kind of computer programming/scripting?
2
~1b[1m~1b[37m *~1b[22m~1b[36m In love with the idea of extending and immersifying the hellworld?
2

2
Send an application to the *prog mailing list and we'll most likely have a good chuckle! Just ~1b[1mtell~1b[22m us a little about your background in games or coding or MUDs or writing, and pitch us an idea or two for what you might want to work on. If we're interested, we'll get back to you! (Note that this we'll get back to you bit is important--if we don't care about your application we just won't respond.)
2

2
GOOD IDEAS:
2

2
~1b[1m~1b[37m *~1b[22m~1b[36m Something already on *ideas that strikes your fancy. (This has 17 upvotes and here's how I want to implement it...)
2
~1b[1m~1b[37m *~1b[22m~1b[36m Tying two previously unconnected areas/NPCs/systems together in a new way. (A journal for helping the mutant firemen put out burning tenements in gangland.)
2
~1b[1m~1b[37m *~1b[22m~1b[36m Extending or detailing an existing area. (The cave complex is basically shit; I want to add a bunch of occult objects, make the altar do interesting things when prayed to...)
2
~1b[1m~1b[37m *~1b[22m~1b[36m ~1b[1mDoing~1b[22m something cool with a currently boring NPC. (Alvin basically does nothing but kill noobs.  What if he had a journal where...)
2
~1b[1m~1b[37m *~1b[22m~1b[36m Adding variety to the item economy. (Alternate heavier, slower, slightly more damaging versions of the following weapons...)
2

2
BAD IDEAS:
2

2
~1b[1m~1b[37m *~1b[22m~1b[36m Huge new areas.'*~1b[22m~1b[36m (So I wanna make a fifteen story building in corpclave with 6 kinds of dudes to kill...)
2
~1b[1m~1b[37m *~1b[22m~1b[36m D&D type shit. (What if magic...was REAL?  And wielded by ELFKIN?)
2
~1b[1m~1b[37m *~1b[22m~1b[36m Superweapons. (So it's like a normal chainsaw lance, but double, you know?)
2
~1b[1m~1b[37m *~1b[22m~1b[36m Grandiose systems with dozens of components.'*~1b[22m~1b[36m (Spaceflight.  You've got your craftable modular spaceships, which of course are built in one of five spaceport cities...)
2
~1b[1m~1b[37m *~1b[22m~1b[36m New stuff that's a lot like stuff we already have. (The Crack Crib!, A cave full of mutant anteaters!, A spooky forest full of ghosts and yetis!)
