WARNING: The HellMOO badmin ~1b[1mexperience~1b[22m is not for everyone. The hellcore is deep and complex, and many people find it intimidating to work with at first. If you're aroused by interconnected dynamic systems, this could be a plus for you. If you aren't a self-motivated curious seeker of wisdom then this may not be for you at all. Remember those nocs you brought to the crossroads?
