This wristpad is what you use to page messages to other players and talk on comm nets such as chatnet.  It's not foolproof -- in some areas (like prison) the signal is blocked.
2

2
To page another player, simply:  'page <person> <some text>'
2

2
See also:  'help radio', 'help communication'
