15
2
A generic creature which does all the shit $monster does, and also looks after any $door. The $gatekeeper will open/close lock/unlock doors in the same room as it if their state varies from the desired state in .guarded_doors.
2

2
$gatekeeper.guarded_doors 
2
     => {{OBJ door_objnum, BOOL open/closed state, BOOL locked/unlocked state}, ...}
2
	1 = open | 0 = closed
2
	1 = locked | 0 = unlocked
2

2
$gatekeeper:_check_door($door) 
2
     - Makes sure a door is in the desired state.
2

2
$gatekeeper:_check_for_guarded_doors() 
2
     - Checks for guarded doors in the .location to possibly rectify.
2

2
$gatekeeper:suggest_next_action()
2
     - Makes a call to :_check_for_guarded_doors.
