2
Makes end-products out of component parts based on a $recipe.  Put all components and the $recipe on the $workbench and do:
2

2
	make <item> with <workbech>
2

2
SEE ALSO: $recipe
2

2
PROPERTIES
2
$workbench.recipe_type => OBJ type
2
	- Accept only recipes of this kind (children of this OBJ)
