"$rpg:report_error(exception, [furtherinfo], [net])";
"When you catch an exception using try-except-endtry, you can send the caught exception variable directly to this function, which will send a traceback to bugnet (a broadcast object). If there is further info you'd like to go with the traceback, you can also provide 'furtherinfo', which can be a string or a list of strings.";
